A user reported to me that the instance I am an administrator of no longer shows the "Bulk Edit" menu item when multi-selecting Issues from the Backlog.

I've never personally used the feature, but I do see in this blog post: http://blogs.atlassian.com/2013/08/jira-agile-tip-of-the-month-bulk-changes/ what they described as their expectation of it.

They (and I obviously) do have the global "Bulk Edit" permission and can still do so from the *search screen*, but the option does not show up as described in that blog post. This was all of a sudden, probably related to the February 15th update.
